title: LF Brisbane based high elo players for tournament
body:
There is a tournament in Brisbane beginning on the 29th of October and I'm looking for Diamond+ Players to form a team.
Please be aware that I am looking for BRISBANE BASED players only.

Send me a msg in game or leave a reply here and I'll add you

Prizes to be aware of:

1st Place: Training Session with the Chiefs in Sydney + $2,000 spending money.
2nd Place: $1,000 budget to split.
3rd Place: Merchandise $1,000 to split.

replies.body: Plat 5 support if that is sufficient enough. Been playing support for 3 years.
I'm Gold V 0lp and haven't really played at all for 3 months, is that ok? pls respond
